ary to prevent or lessen any unlawful or harmful actions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. UPDATING PERSONAL INFORMATION<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you would like to update or correct any of your personal information held by Orascom Construction, kindly contact Orascom Construction\u2019s Investor Relations department at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:ir@orascom.com\">ir@orascom.com<\/a>&nbsp;and we will endeavour to update and correct your personal information.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. NON-WARRANTY<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>5.1 If you disclose any personal information to a third party, such as one of Orascom Construction&#8217;s affiliates or an entity which operates a website linked to this website or anyone other than Orascom Construction you must be aware that Orascom Construction does not regulate or control how that third party uses your personal information. You should always ensure that you read the privacy policy of any third party, as their privacy policy will be applicable.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>5.2 Where your personal information is accessed or used by a third party through the Orascom Construction website, you will release Orascom Construction from any liability, financial or physical as a result of the use of such information. You will also release Orascom Construction from the obligation to pay you any benefits or profits gained by any third parties as a result of the use of your personal information obtained via Orascom Construction\u2019s website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>6. ASSENT TO TERMS OF PRIVACY POLICY<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>By using the Orascom Construction website you acknowledge that you have read the terms of this privacy policy and that you agree to the use of User Data for the purposes set out above. Please note that Orascom Construction may amend this Privacy Policy at any time.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>1. CONFIDENTIALITY Any information, which 